🐸 The Frogots 🐸
This frogot, frogot that he was a frog and decided to go as a frog this Halloween...
🔸🔸🔸
Halloween limited edition mystery bags available now.
Frob packs pins of his friends and family, but he can't remember what's in what bag, so it's a mystery what you'll get!
5 Halloween Frogots to collect 🎃
.

❗❗follow the Kickstarter link in bio to get notified of launch❗❗
Soy the baby penguin was meant to launch next week, but I think we will be postponing it, we will see how we feel as my daughter wants to be active in promoting her to raise funds to save the penguins.
I also have ideas for some other cute hooded bird plushie stretch goals.
.
.
.

❗NEW PRODUCT❗
This Friday our Pumpkin Patch pants presale drops!
We are still new to clothing and are using presales to fund manufacturing 🎃 
.
Ordering the presale guarantees your size!!
.
Good news, the manufacturing time isn't so long, please note we can't guarantee these before Halloween - but when does Halloween end REALLY??
.
Thank you to everyone who supports our clothing range, we have two more pieces coming this Friday also!
.
Everything is in place to go ahead with Fridays drop, we are still recovering from covid but hoping to be feeling better by next week 🤞🤞
Please understand there are delays in pin club post and email replies due to this.
.
.
.
